  "title": "Site Supervisor Civil",
  "description": "<h5><u><strong>Job Responsibilities :</strong></u></h5>\n<p>1. Overall reporting to Project Manager.</p>\n<p>2. Responsible for scheduling and daily site activities.</p>\n<p>3. Managing workers, liaise and coordinate with clients and sub contractors.</p>\n<p>4. Ensuring environmental, safety and health aspect on site.</p>\n<p><u><strong>Job requirement :</strong></u></p>\n<p>1. Diploma in Civil &amp; Structural Engineering or construction related study.</p>\n<p>2. Able to use Microsoft Office.</p>\n<p>3. Positive working attitute.</p>\n<p>4. Good interpersonal and analytical skills.</p>\n<p>5. With or without experience are welcome.</p>",
